1
00:00:01,105 --> 00:00:06,695
Where are you going to spend your holidays this year, Gary?
Gary,今年你们打算去哪里度假?

2
00:00:06,872 --> 00:00:08,976
We may go abroad.
我们可能到国外去,

3
00:00:09,128 --> 00:00:10,735
I'm not sure.
但我不敢肯定.

4
00:00:11,061 --> 00:00:14,138
My wife wants to go to Egypt.
我妻子想到埃及去,

5
00:00:14,530 --> 00:00:16,940
I'd like to go there, too.
我也想去那儿.

6
00:00:17,702 --> 00:00:20,477
We can't make up our minds.
我们还拿不定主意.

7
00:00:20,777 --> 00:00:24,676
Will you travel by sea or by air?
你们乘船去,还是乘飞机去? 

8
00:00:24,964 --> 00:00:27,502
We may travel by sea.
我们可能乘船去.

9
00:00:27,881 --> 00:00:30,157
It's cheaper, isn't it?
这更便宜些,不是吗?

10
00:00:30,703 --> 00:00:33,606
I'm sure you'll enjoy yourselves.
我肯定你们一定会玩得很愉快.

11
00:00:34,213 --> 00:00:36,025
Don't be so sure.
别那么肯定.

12
00:00:36,752 --> 00:00:39,196
We might not go anywhere.
我们可能哪里也去不成.

13
00:00:39,775 --> 00:00:43,228
My wife always worries too much.
我妻子总是担心这担心那的.

14
00:00:43,909 --> 00:00:46,953
Who's going to look after the dog?
谁来照看狗啦,

15
00:00:47,446 --> 00:00:50,650
Who's going to look after the house?
谁来看管房子啦,

16
00:00:51,132 --> 00:00:54,262
Who's going to look after the garden?
谁来照料花园啦,

17
00:00:55,031 --> 00:00:58,054
We have this problem every year.
我们每年都碰到这个问题.

18
00:00:58,988 --> 00:01:04,023
In the end, we stay at home and look after everything!
最后,我们呆在家里来照看一切.

